# 🎯 Why Good Students Get Rejected

Many students think:

> "If I know technical concepts, I'll get selected."

Not always.

Companies also evaluate:

✅ Communication
✅ Confidence
✅ Problem-solving approach
✅ Teamwork
✅ Attitude

---

# 📄 1️⃣ What is ATS?

ATS = Applicant Tracking System

It is software used by companies to filter resumes.

---

### What ATS Does

Suppose 1000 students apply.

Recruiters cannot read all resumes.

ATS scans:

* Skills
* Keywords
* Experience
* Projects

---

### Example

If job requires:

```text
Python
SQL
REST APIs
Git
```

And your resume contains them,

✅ Higher chance of being shortlisted.

---

# 🎯 ATS Resume Rule

Don't write:

❌ Good at programming

Write:

✅ Python, SQL, REST APIs, Git, Computer Networks

